{"tid":2224310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大生重建連儂牆 籲關注12手足","createTime":"2020-09-30T11:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:01:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6e3d60fc33cbdeb066a254da3488c83a381bb6","tid":2224310,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/ENWU5UJBZFABZJT7PCVMFUUMSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FENWU5UJBZFABZJT7PCVMFUUMSY%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=80440b9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FENWU5UJBZFABZJT7PCVMFUUMSY%2F&h=0e87f711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/ENWU5UJBZFABZJT7PCVMFUUMSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港大生重建連儂牆 籲關注12手足<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上周六晚一批「藍絲」闖入港大撕毀連儂牆，在場保安員並無阻止，校方亦沒即時報案，引起港大學生不滿。港大學生會昨日發起重建連儂牆，學生自備多款文宣貼滿四幅連儂牆，明言「誓捍表達自由」，又張貼大型海報關注被扣內地的12名港青，包括港大生郭子麟，同時有學生在校園內噴上12人名字，籲勿忘手足。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中聯辦未審先判：犯罪事實清楚<br />\n<br />\n港大連儂牆被破壞後，校方前日發電郵指檢討事件及校園管理安排後，已就事件報警，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bnNWY4xlQMD7ZArYUE9KB1jPZcI=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FYFNID3P5NGYTMFPXHQ4NPM57U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbnNWY4xlQMD7ZArYUE9KB1jPZcI%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFYFNID3P5NGYTMFPXHQ4NPM57U.jpg&h=8d2e106e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大學生會昨發起重建連儂牆行動，學生帶同多款文宣，貼滿上周六被藍絲破壞的連儂牆。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生會促張翔譴責暴徒<br />\n<br />\n重建大學街上層的連儂牆前夕，已有學生率先貼上文宣，包括「這裡是香港大學」、「有本事就考入来」、「你仔女考得到来？」至下午1時，不少港大教職員及學生清理連儂牆上的舊紙屑痕迹，重新貼上多款新文宣，包括大型海報「十二手足 生死未卜」、「save 12 HK youth」等，列出12人名字，以英文簡述他們在內地被扣押，被拒與受委託律師接觸，面對不公平對待，更備註指郭子麟為港大工程系學生，惜校方一直未為其發聲。另有「香港人，別放棄 請你們堅持到最後一刻 十月一 荃灣見」等文宣。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會會長葉芷琳強調，連儂牆是港大生言論自由指標，不會妥協，「Lunch哥」亦現身支持。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其間，學生會成員到達鈕魯詩樓表達三大訴求，包括要求校長張翔譴責毀連儂牆的暴徒；。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有港大生於校園大學街沿途，噴上12名被扣內地港青名字，又在人流最多的香港大學站A2出口對開，噴上港大工程系一年級生郭子麟名字，籲大家勿忘手足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kxeBT5hql5fgrL1x6Pr00tXwQ1c=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KDDF2GDGGVAGVHUABG7LVEZ2BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkxeBT5hql5fgrL1x6Pr00tXwQ1c%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKDDF2GDGGVAGVHUABG7LVEZ2BE.jpg&h=af2007e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有學生貼上「十二手足 生死未卜」文宣，籲勿忘12名被內地扣押港青。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/87G07bSjPT61e9afZ0s_R3AsFlE=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5NMJISXRRVCOHMTB36QZXXHCMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F87G07bSjPT61e9afZ0s_R3AsFlE%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5NMJISXRRVCOHMTB36QZXXHCMQ.jpg&h=31faea09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■學生會到達鈕魯詩樓表達訴求，被多名保安組成人鏈擋在大樓外。"},{"pid":"b4352f2df193e6d8442a7833ec90137d95dff116","tid":2224310,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}